Install & Usage
________________________________________________________________________

git clone https://github.com/imlinus/ascii-font
cd ascii-font/
chmod +x ./ascii-font

./ascii-font hello-world


Contribute
________________________________________________________________________

If you have an idea on how to improve the font, then please fork the
repository and add your pull request

Q definitely needs some love for example
Or perhaps some special symbols or numbers

